headline: Paycom (PAYC) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of HR software provider Paycom (NYSE:PAYC) jumped 3% in the afternoon session after BTIG initiated coverage on the software company with a "Buy" rating and set a price target of $195.
